"<3.so>My husband was the first voe to ever\n"
"tell me I was beautiful...<4.pa>\n"
"\n"
"I love him so! And so I need those \n"
"<5.se_co>Molduga guts<6.re_co>, no matter what... <7.so>But... \n"
