msgctxt "Talk_06"
msgid ""
"<1.se_co><2.so><3.re_co>The <4.se_co>Molduga<5.re_co> is a monster... A "
"terror\n"
"so savage that even other monsters \n"
"won't approach it...\n"
"It's often been spotted west of here, in\n"
"the <6.se_co>Toruma Dunes<7.re_co>, and in the south.\n"
"\n"
"It's very <8.se_co>sensitive to vibrations<9.re_co>, and it\n"
"tends to attack anything that draws near.\n"
"\n"
"<10.so>You can't approach it or even move\n"
"near it...<11.pa> And you can't use someone\n"
"as bait...\n"
"So what am I to do..."
msgstr ""

